# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../contributing.rst:22
msgid "Contributing"
msgstr "Doprinos"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../contributing.rst:24
msgid ""
"Want to help improve OpenShot (*and make some friends in the process*)? "
"Please consider joining our open-source team by filling out this quick "
"`contributor form <https://forms.gle/CRqkS5tLMJE1V36V8>`_ and introduce "
"yourself! All volunteers are welcome, regardless of skills or skill level. "
"**Let's build something amazing!**"
msgstr ""
"Želite li pomoći u poboljšanju OpenShota (*i pritom steći nove prijatelje*)? "
"Razmislite o pridruživanju našem open-source timu ispunjavanjem ovog brzog "
"`obrasca za suradnike <https://forms.gle/CRqkS5tLMJE1V36V8>`_ i predstavite "
"se! Svi volonteri su dobrodošli, bez obzira na vještine ili razinu znanja. "
"**Izgradimo nešto nevjerojatno!**"

